  "texts": [
    "Here, the required EMG, motion sensors, and Brain-Computer Interfaces (BCI) were acquired from the standard resources, and pre-processing procedures were used to eliminate the unwanted information.",
    "Decoding procedures were employed for the validation.",
    "Later, essential features were collected to generate the dependencies among the stimuli and also to collect the response from the central nervous system.",
    "Further, several experimental validations were executed to compute the prediction effectualness of the suggested framework.",
    "Wang et al."
  ]
